r.gov/ahps2/forecasts.php?wfo=cae">River Forecasts (Map)</a>                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="http://waterwatch.usgs.gov/?m=real&w=gmap&regions=sc">Current & Past Streamflow</a>                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="https://www.weather.gov/erh/mmefs">Ensemble River Guidance</a>                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="https://water.weather.gov/ahps/rfc/rfc.php">River Forecast Centers</a>                        </li>                    </ul>                </div>            </li>            <li>                <div class="subMenuNavList section-link">                    <a href="https://www.weather.gov/wrh/Climate?wfo=cae">Climate and Past Weather</a>                </div>                <div class="sub">                    <ul>                        <li>                            <a href="https://www.weather.gov/wrh/Climate?wfo=cae">Past Observed Weather</a>                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="https://forecast.weather.gov/product.php?site=CAE&issuedby=CAE&product=RTP">24 Hour Summary</a>                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="https://www.cocorahs.org/">CoCoRaHS</a>                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="https://water.weather.gov/precip">Past Rainfall</a>                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="https://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/snow-and-ice/">Snowfall Records</a>                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="https://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/products/expert_assessment/sdo_summary.php">Drought Outlook</a>                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="https://www.weather.gov/wrh/Climate?wfo=cae">Historical Records</a>                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="https://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/">Climate Prediction</a>                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="https://www.weather.gov/cae/TropicalEventSummary">Tropical Cyclone Reports</a>                        </li>                    </ul>                </div>            </li>            <li>                <div class="subMenuNavList section-link">                    <a href="http://www.weather.gov/cae/office.html">Local Programs</a>                </div>                <div class="sub">                    <ul>                        <li>                            <a href="http://www.weather.gov/cae/outreach.html">Outreach</a>                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="http://www.weather.gov/cae/nwr.html">NWR</a>                        </li>                        <li>                            <a href="http://www.weather.gov/cae/skywarn.html">Skywarn</a>                        </li>                    </ul>                </div>            </li>        </ul>    </div></div>

                            
                            
                            
