			<td align="center" valign="top" width="540">
			<h2 align="center"><font face="Arial">2024 Columbia Metro Climate Plots</font></h2>

			<p><font face="Arial">Climate data on this page is PRELIMINARY (unofficial). CERTIFIED (official) climate data is available from the <a href="https://www.ncdc.noaa.gov" title="National Climatic Data Center (NCDC)">National Climatic Data Center (NCDC)</a>. </font></p>

			<p>&nbsp;</p>

